items.title: India could benefit from free trade in long term: Mercedes-Benz India MD & CEO
items.description: In FY25, the overall luxury car segment is estimated to be at over 51,500 units compared to about 49,800 units in FY24.

items.title: Apple India produces $22 billion of iPhones in shift from China
items.description: The ramp-up suggests the iPhone maker and its suppliers are accelerating a pivot to India from China, a process it began when harsh Covid lockdowns hurt production at Apple’s largest plant.
